<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Rozlutskyi Art</title>
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(to right, #e63946, #f1faee, #1d3557);
      color: #ffffff;
      text-align: center;
    }
    header {
      padding: 60px 20px;
    }
    h1 {
      font-size: 3em;
      margin-bottom: 0.2em;
    }
    p {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto 2em auto;
      font-size: 1.2em;
    }
    .gallery {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 15px;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .gallery img {
      max-width: 300px;
      width: 100%;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
    }
    .about {
      padding: 40px 20px;
      background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
    }
    .about h2 {
      font-size: 2em;
      margin-bottom: 0.5em;
    }
    .about p {
      max-width: 700px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      font-size: 1.1em;
    }
    .links {
      margin-top: 30px;
    }
    .links a {
      color: #f1faee;
      margin: 0 10px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: bold;
      border: 2px solid #f1faee;
      padding: 8px 14px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      transition: background 0.3s, color 0.3s;
    }
    .links a:hover {
      background: #f1faee;
      color: #1d3557;
    }
    footer {
      margin-top: 40px;
      padding: 20px;
      font-size: 0.9em;
      background-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <h1>Rozlutskyi Art</h1>
    <p>Ukrainian soul meets global vision. Mural art, color, and transformation — by Andrii Rozlutskyi.</p>
  </header>

  <section class="gallery">
    <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/300x200.png?text=Art+1" alt="Artwork 1">
    <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/300x200.png?text=Art+2" alt="Artwork 2">
    <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/300x200.png?text=Art+3" alt="Artwork 3">
  </section>

  <section class="about">
    <h2>About the Artist</h2>
    <p>Andrii Rozlutskyi is a Ukrainian artist, cultural activist, and creator of the Rozlutskyi Art brand. His works blend traditional Ukrainian motifs with contemporary expression, offering a unique visual journey rooted in heritage and transformation. Now based in Canada, he continues to share his vibrant vision with the world.</p>
    <div class="links">
      <a href="https://www.instagram.com/" target="_blank">Instagram</a>
      <a href="https://www.youtube.com/" target="_blank">YouTube</a>
      <a href="https://www.etsy.com/" target="_blank">Etsy</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <footer>
    &copy; 2025 Rozlutskyi Art | Created with ❤️ for artistic freedom
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
